title: Britain and the EU
itunes:author: Dr Maja Kluger Rasmussen
description: Contributor(s): Dr Maja Kluger Rasmussen | Dr Maja Rasmussen of the LSE discusses the current feeling in Britain towards the EU and possibilities for the future if Britain decides to change its relationship with the EU.
